---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title='About DevPath' permalink={'/about'}>
  <!-- Hero Section with Author -->
  <div class='relative border-b border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface/50 to-transparent'>
    <div class='container relative py-12 sm:py-20'>
      <div class='mx-auto max-w-5xl'>
        <div class='flex flex-col items-center gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:gap-12'>
          <!-- Author Image -->
          <div class='relative flex-shrink-0'>
            <div class='absolute -inset-1 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent opacity-20 blur-xl'></div>
            <img
              src='/authors/IMG_3110.jpg'
              class='relative h-32 w-32 rounded-2xl border-2 border-white/10 object-cover sm:h-44 sm:w-44'
              alt='Jean Michel Eid'
            />
          </div>
          
          <!-- Author Info -->
          <div class='flex-1 text-center sm:text-left'>
            <div class='mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary ring-1 ring-primary/20'>
              <div class='h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary'></div>
              About DevPath
            </div>
            
            <h1 class='mb-4 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl'>
              <span class='hidden sm:inline'>Hello, </span>I'm Jean Michel Eid
            </h1>
            
            <p class='mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted sm:text-lg'>
              I created DevPath to help developers find their path if they are
              confused and help them learn and grow in their career.
            </p>
            
            <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row'>
              <a
                class='btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium'
                target='_blank'
                href='https://github.com/jm961'
              >
                <svg class='h-4 w-4' fill='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
                  <path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z' clip-rule='evenodd'></path>
                </svg>
                <span>GitHub</span>
              </a>
              
              <a
                class='btn-ghost inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium'
                target='_blank'
                href='mailto:jeanmicheleid@gmail.com'
              >
                <svg class='h-4 w-4' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
                  <path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' stroke-width='2' d='M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z'></path>
                </svg>
                <span class='hidden sm:inline'>jeanmicheleid@gmail.com</span>
                <span class='inline sm:hidden'>Email</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class='bg-gradient-to-b from-bg to-surface/30 py-12 sm:py-20'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='mx-auto max-w-4xl'>
        <main id='main-content' class='space-y-8'>
          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>What is DevPath?</h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                <span class='font-bold text-white'>DevPath</span> contains community-curated
                roadmaps, study plans, paths, and resources for developers. There are
                role-based roadmaps, listing skills you should for any given role, as
                well as skill-based roadmaps listing items to learn for any given skill.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>How are roadmaps created?</h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                Roadmaps are created by researching market demand and listening to user requests. We do the heavy lifting and research so you can enjoy having a comprehensive roadmap with the best curated resources, without having to search through countless websites yourself.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>
              What are the plans for DevPath?
            </h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                Our long-term plan is to make DevPath a go-to place for
                developers whenever they plan on learning something new. We started
                with roadmaps, guides, videos and other visual content but we plan
                on introducing best practices, best-practices for certain tasks, quizzes
                to test your knowledge and prepare yourself for the interviews,
                project ideas to work on while following the roadmaps, public
                profiles to share your progress and interact with the other learners
                and so on.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>How is DevPath built?</h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                The website is built with <a
                  href='https://astro.build/'
                  class='font-semibold text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent/50'
                  target='_blank'
                  rel='nofollow'>Astro</a
                > and <a
                  href='https://tailwindcss.com/'
                  class='font-semibold text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent/50'
                  target='_blank'
                  rel='nofollow'>Tailwind</a
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>How can I add a new roadmap?</h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                For new roadmaps, you can reach out to <a
                  class='font-semibold text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent/50'
                  href='mailto:jeanmicheleid@gmail.com'
                  target='_blank'>jeanmicheleid@gmail.com</a> and suggest your topic. If you're an expert in the field or have valuable resources to share, I'm always open to collaborating to make our content even better.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>
              How can I update an existing roadmap?
            </h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                If you have suggestions for improving an existing roadmap or think something can be better, please reach out to <a
                  class='font-semibold text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent/50'
                  href='mailto:jeanmicheleid@gmail.com'
                  target='_blank'>jeanmicheleid@gmail.com</a> with your ideas. I welcome all feedback and suggestions to make our roadmaps more comprehensive and helpful.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-surface/50 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8'>
            <h2 class='mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl'>
              What is the best way to contact you?
            </h2>
            <div class='space-y-4 text-muted'>
              <p>
                Feel free to send me an email at
                <a
                  class='font-semibold text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent/50'
                  href='mailto:jeanmicheleid@gmail.com'
                  target='_blank'>jeanmicheleid@gmail.com</a
                >. I get lots of messages, so apologies in advance if you don't hear
                back from me right away, but I do my best to reply to everyone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
